{"tid":209661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登就係世界中心！世界偉人盡在此地！","createTime":"2017-04-20T11:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T12:58:40.000Z","uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6805bc589b41ee4e1c957820633a13036b0719","tid":209661,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"呢度人材背出<br />\n<br />\n個個月入50k以上<br />\n<br />\n話屌邊條女就屌邊條女<br />\n<br />\n邊條女做雞又一眼睇出<br />\n<br />\n早排又拆穿捐肛既陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957a4e10166cff0a4c96f1bdb8c8de0c4562cd9f","tid":209661,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"樓主做高級物業看更日日睇住啲名流出出入入梗係睇唔起連登廢青啦"},{"pid":"92fe9ff1ac576f725900325e683e8b7aa7863eb0","tid":209661,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"係「人材輩出」呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做保安都要不忘進修呀。"},{"pid":"c2a11888f4f10180260bf4911390949d6f7f5fef","tid":209661,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/203961/page/13?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/203961/page/13?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"6e231ca2547fc9690fc526f79235619191fb8712","tid":209661,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇簡介<br />\n係咪上次吹到好勁一開波就捐錢點知比人反cup個2個</blockquote><br />\n劇情回顧:<br />\n屈機男在高登常以有錢佬姿態教化高登仔做人道理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0i1Q28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0i1Q28.jpg&h=c884d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男常自稱有幾個物業, 但又睇淡樓市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1Bp683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1Bp683.jpg&h=14ab5e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69n6byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69n6byc.jpg&h=508c64cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈機男以高高在上姿態雄霸財經台, 而且有一眾信眾追隨.<br />\n然而, 直至會員 米已成炊出現, 他質疑屈機男之有錢言論, 多次挑戰其財經台權威.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u76373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u76373.jpg&h=476a844a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是大發明家屈機男發明了解決糾紛方法...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly869i3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy869i3.jpg&h=be0daf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男及其信眾一直強勢, 欺侮米已成炊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKrCVnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKrCVnV.jpg&h=33bd4d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgX65WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgX65WO.jpg&h=c0ddb46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVg6J3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVg6J3M.jpg&h=f50358a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係直接飛到結局.... 屈機男捐唔起錢認輸, 而其信眾亦鳥獸散或深潛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6d859G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6d859G.jpg&h=bb060f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1pgUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1pgUy.jpg&h=7c7dbc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8NL1v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8NL1v6.png&h=401336d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3b4251dd76266d82725684c920524a5bd381c95f","tid":209661,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>走數狗屈機男 信佢果個真係要驗腦</blockquote><br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先ko左件阿域<br />\n<br />\n另外，我走左邊條數？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/009PHw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F009PHw5.jpg&h=dcad78a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明話輸左永久退出高登, 但又定期上水留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Opwr82D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpwr82D.jpg&h=d8cfee9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走數狗屈機男 信佢果個真係要驗腦</blockquote><br />\n自己言而無信，偏偏寫文成日廢up教人做人要上進反省<br />\n垃圾就是垃圾<br />\n笑話永遠係笑話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"212d10f94eaaf4517bbbe8a8ac979641572d88ef","tid":209661,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627b3d46e9973ea3ed7df7b7c800fbb1a279c1b2","tid":209661,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醜唔醜阿你"},{"pid":"a7a3f79f4f05bc345473b876081b6d62ee5ae904","tid":209661,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"又出一批大哲學家<br />\n<br />\n探討人性黑暗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  世間冇好人好事 只有利益行頭"},{"pid":"ad26cdf59292c9d28005eccb413bb104bd3cc5c1","tid":209661,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又出一批大哲學家<br />\n<br />\n探討人性黑暗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  世間冇好人好事 只有利益行頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大帽山結冰有人被困，小食停通宵供應熱食 -&gt; 為錢為利益，發災難財<br />\n大學生求換心 -&gt; 抵死，食得女多MK有報應<br />\n中年女人求換肝 -&gt; 抵死，早死早著<br />\n善心女捐肝救人 -&gt; 遲下有後遺症，為錢為利益為光環<br />\n<br />\n每次有關於好人好事既新聞<br />\n<br />\n連登仔都帶比我全新既哲學思考角度同大道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擴闊我對人性既理解同認知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b998e578e026b8bf45a9b4c53dda7bd8a0127d3","tid":209661,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25497cc2562b04e9b3a41b310d5d5ece90f2b1f9","tid":209661,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fa7f67ac0fd061037f8db83d41ac1de2535465","tid":209661,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屈機男好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n走數狗屈機男果然係厚顏無恥，呢樣佢真係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fde4ac003a7bfe667e086b3c8c02fdcbbd4022","tid":209661,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"被屈機男🤣"}]}